Author: Svandis
Title: [BOUNTY] Svandis - Research and Visualisation platform for crypto traders
Body: Dear participants of Svandis Ambassador Campaign!  We have decided to stop the Twitter and Telegram part of the Ambassador Campaign. We closed new registrations on September 28, 9:00 AM UTC.  We were delighted to see so many people joining our chatroom and Twitter! However, if we keep the Telegram/Twitter parts open, the individual reward will be eventually diluted too much. You are always welcome to join other areas of our Ambassador Campaign - Content and BitcointalkSignatures! Moreover, keep an eye to our news - after the platform release you will be able to run Svandis DataMiningApp (currently under closed community testing) to get rewards in SVN.    What does it mean for the current participants of the Telegram/Twitter Campaigns? 1. We will no longer add stakes for any further actions in the Chatroom or Twitter. All stakes will be added after proceeding whole list of all participants. 2. However, the participants are still required to be in the chat until the end of Svandis Token Sale - we will have to disqualify those who leave the chat ahead of the time. Same with twitter - you need to keep following Svandis official twitter (you may not have retweets/tweets thought). 3. Our Bounty Management team will carefully check the participants in order to exclude bots and violators. 4. We will do these checks up until the final distribution of the stakes which will happen soon after the Token Sale finishes.    Tokens for all campaigns will be distributed as soon as they will be issued and unlocked - after the Token Sale.  Thank you all for joining the campaign!

Body: In an age of data overload, volume doesn’t necessarily mean value. At Svandis, we are revolutionising the way you receive information. By taking the most effective solutions from traditional markets and adapting them to the demands of the crypto markets, our platform provides the tools you need to make more insightful trading and investment decisions in the volatile world of digital assets.      Svandis Ambassador Campaign   We are offering our participants a total allocation of 1% from our overall token supply. The total number of tokens in circulation may vary (depending on the actual amount contributed during the Token Sale; max total token supply is 400,000,000 tokens, while price of 1 token is $0.05 and max hard cap is $12,000,000; thus up to $200,000 in Svandis tokens might be distributed between participants), but in any case 1% of issued tokens will still be designated to the Ambassador campaign.  Every user can register for the program only once; multiple accounts will be discovered and disqualified!  Ambassador campaign members, who use unfair methods, such as spam and fake Likes and Shares, are to be excluded from Ambassador campaigns and will not receive any rewards.  Important note: due to legal reasons we can’t offer our tokens for citizens, permanent residents and owners of primary residence or domicile in the United States of America (including Puerto Rico, U.S. Virgin Islands or any other U.S. possessions). We also can’t send our tokens to citizens and permanent residents of China. We will not be able to send you your reward if you belong to any of the categories stated above! You may be requested to pass KYC procedure!  The Ambassador Campaign starts from the moment this post is published and lasts until the end of the Token Sale.     Ambassador Campaign Pool Allocation:      General Ambassador Rules 1. All Ambassador Campaign Participants are required to join Svandis Telegram group: https://t.me/svandis_chatroom 2. The Team reserve their right to make changes to the terms in any moment 3. Payment addresses will NOT be changed after submission 4. Team decisions are final 5. Quoting of Past Reports will not be accepted in All Campaigns 6. Read the rules carefully    40% of the Ambassador pool to be allocated to the Content campaign. We are interested in quality articles, blog posts, videos and other publications in different  languages. All publications should be original and will be measured by their quality, length, audience and creativity and will get from 1 to 10 stakes accordingly. All written materials must be above 2,500 characters while videos must be longer than 3 minutes.  For example, you can write articles or make videos about our products, or you can conduct an analysis of the Whitepaper, competitors etc.  Each campaign member should make at least 1 (one) publication before the Token Sale starts.  Each member should go through registration. Please note that we have the right to not approve your content and assign 0 stakes. Kindly note that the audience of the participant (namely, size and quality) is the major factor for approval or disapproval.
